          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>
                                        <date>den 12 <add>?</add> May <hi rend="underline"
                                                  >1849</hi></date>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <addressee>Mr I Leeser Rev.</addressee>
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <add>סופר ומוכר ספרים</add>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <persName role="author">Nathan Ottinger</persName>
                                        <add>Hebrew</add>
                              </p>
                              <p><placeName>Pitt street No 87</placeName>.</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p>Minister of the congregation of
                                                  Mikveh=<lb/><placeName>Israel</placeName></p>
                              <p>
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="3"/>
                              <p><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>12<hi rend="sup">th</hi>
                                                  May, 1849</date>.</p>
                              <p>Mr. <sic>J.</sic>
                                        <addressee>Leeser Rev.</addressee>
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">Although</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)"><del>?</del> I have already sold a<lb/> good many
                                        of your prayer books “Dibrei Zadikim”, which I have
                                        ob-<lb/>tained from <persName>Mr. Goldstein</persName>, I
                                        sold them at a very small profit. It is generally known that
                                        it is possible to obtain the same prayer<lb/> books in
                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> at $2., while
                                        until now I have had to pay<lb/>
                                        <persName>Mr. Goldstein</persName> $2.25. I therefore take
                                        the liberty to drop you these<lb/> lines in order to inquire
                                        whether I could not have them at a lower<lb/> price either
                                        from you or through you, so that I might be able to<lb/>
                                        compete against every other tradesman. In that event I
                                        should<lb/> certainly be able to use more of them. I should
                                        also like to know<lb/> the price of our
                                                  <sic>Pentatuechs</sic> and other books. With
                                        regard to this<lb/> please answer me in the near future. As
                                        to my character, please<lb/> inquire of <persName>Mr.
                                                  Isaacs</persName>, or anyone else in this
                                        town.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">With best wishes, and sincerely,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">
                                        <persName role="author">Nathan Ottinger</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">(Scribe and Book-seller)</p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">
                                        <placeName>Pitt St. No. 87</placeName>
                              </p>
                    </body>
